<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Standard Card</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use for browsable content that requires action — article feeds or general programme listings without structured metadata. Pairs a body (title, description, meta chip) with an actions row. Best displayed in 2–4 column grids.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview">
    <div class="ds-preview__content">
      <div class="card" style="max-width: 340px;">
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">Business Management BA (Hons)</h3>
          <p class="card__description">Develop practical business skills and strategic thinking in the heart of London.</p>
          <div class="card__meta">
            <span class="chip chip--green">Undergraduate</span>
            <span>3 years full-time</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">Apply Now</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Course Card — Brand</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use on programme directory pages and search results where each card represents a full degree or course entry. The brand-green surface signals a primary, clickable listing. The chip identifies the study level, the meta grid surfaces the three facts a prospective student needs at a glance (UCAS code, intake, duration), and the dual CTAs let users apply immediately or read more. Display in 2–3 column grids on desktop; single-column on mobile.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--dark">
    <div class="ds-preview__content" style="gap: var(--sp-24); align-items: stretch;">
      <div class="card card--course" style="max-width: 360px;">
        <div class="card__chips">
          <span class="chip chip--white">BA Hons</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="card__title">International Business BA (Hons)</h3>
        <p class="card__desc">Develop the skills to lead and innovate in international business with a global perspective.</p>
        <div class="card__course-meta">
          <div class="card__meta-item">
            <span class="card__meta-label">UCAS</span>
            <span class="card__meta-value">N120</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card__meta-item">
            <span class="card__meta-label">Intake</span>
            <span class="card__meta-value">September 2025</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card__meta-item">
            <span class="card__meta-label">Duration</span>
            <span class="card__meta-value">3 years full-time</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card__actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn--primary-inverted btn--sm">Apply Now</a>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn--secondary-inverted btn--sm">View Course Details</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
