  <p class="docs-section__description">Use the light sub-variant when the Course Card appears on a white or off-white page background where a solid brand-green card would be too heavy. The white surface keeps the card legible without losing the structured metadata layout. A coloured chip (green for undergraduate, violet for postgraduate, etc.) provides the degree-level signal. Use consistently within a grid — do not mix Brand and Light variants in the same card row.</p>
