  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Related Course Card — Brand</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use to surface related or recommended courses within a course detail page, school page, or subject area listing. The absence of a description paragraph keeps the card compact and scannable — users in this context are already familiar with the degree level and are choosing between options, not discovering them for the first time. Place in a 2–3 column row beneath the main course content, or in a sidebar on wide layouts.</p>
