<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Feature Cards</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use to highlight key selling points, statistics, or benefits — typically in a 3-column row on landing pages or section intros. Colour variants (Yellow, Violet, Peach) create visual rhythm; avoid mixing more than three accent colours in a single row.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview">
    <div class="ds-preview__content">
      <div class="card card--feature card--feature-yellow" style="max-width: 280px;">
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">World-Class Faculty</h3>
          <p class="card__description">Learn from industry leaders and renowned academics.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--feature card--feature-violet" style="max-width: 280px;">
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">Global Community</h3>
          <p class="card__description">Students from 140+ nationalities on campus.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--feature card--feature-peach" style="max-width: 280px;">
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">London Location</h3>
          <p class="card__description">Study in Regent's Park, a Royal Park of London.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Dark Feature Card</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use on dark-background sections where light feature cards would lack contrast. Well-suited for partnership logos, award callouts, or accreditations displayed against a charcoal or deep brand surface.</p>
  <div class="ds-preview ds-preview--dark">
    <div class="ds-preview__content">
